#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; provides you with all kinds of information about the Periodic "
"Table of the Elements. You can lookup lots of information about the elements "
"and also use visualizations to show them. It is free and licensed under the "
"&GNU; Public License."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; vsebuje vse vrste informacij o periodnem sistemu elementov. "
"Poiščete lahko veliko informacij o elementih in jih prikažete z "
"vizualizacijami. Je brezplačen in licenciran pod &GNU; Javno licenco."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can visualize the Periodic Table of the Elements by groups, blocks, and "
"families. You can plot data for a range of elements for properties like the "
"boiling point or the atomic mass. You can go back in time and see what "
"elements were known at a given date. You can also calculate the molecular "
"mass of molecules."
msgstr ""
"Periodni sistem elementov lahko predstavite po skupinah, blokih in družinah. "
"Za vrsto elementov lahko narišete podatke o lastnostih, kot sta vrelišče ali "
"atomska masa. Lahko se vrnete v preteklost in preverite, kateri elementi so "
"bili znani na določen datum. Izračunate lahko tudi molekulsko maso molekul."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; quick start guide"
msgstr "&kalzium; priročnik za hitri zagon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is &kalzium; the first time you run it, either by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Applications</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Education</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Science</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>&kalzium;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the application starter or with <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> and entering "
"<command>kalzium</command> into the input field."
msgstr ""
"To je &kalzium; prvič, ko ga zaženete tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Aplikacije</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izobraževanje</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Znanost</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>&kalzium;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz začetnega programa ali z <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> in v vnosno polje vnesete "
"<command>kalzium</command>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kalzium; main window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kalzium; glavno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kalzium; main window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kalzium; glavno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; is divided in an information panel on the left (in red), the table "
"view (in blue) which shows the elements of the periodic table, and a legend "
"panel at the bottom (in green). The standard menubar allows you to choose "
"what you want to display and the status bar reports facts. The table view "
"and the panels can be hidden using the corresponding items in <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> menu. For example, you can hide the information panel with "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Information</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; je razdeljen na informacijsko ploščo na levi strani (v rdeči "
"barvi), pregled tabele (v modri barvi), ki prikazuje elemente periodnega "
"sistema, in ploščo z legendo na dnu (v zeleni barvi). V standardni menijski "
"vrstici lahko izberete, kaj želite prikazati, vrstica stanja pa poroča o "
"dejstvih. Pogled tabele in plošče lahko skrijete z uporabo ustreznih "
"elementov v meniju <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu>. Informacijsko ploščo lahko na "
"primer skrijete z <menuchoice> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Podatki</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you move the mouse cursor on an element of the table, an overview of "
"the current element is displayed in the <guilabel>Overview</guilabel> tab of "
"the information panel."
msgstr ""
"Ko se s kazalcem miške premaknete na element tabele, se v zavihku "
"<guilabel>Pregled</guilabel> informacijske plošče prikaže pregled trenutnega "
"elementa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose several views for the table: classic periodic table, short "
"periodic table, long periodic table, &etc; It is also possible to change "
"numeration scheme or display the elements per families, per groups, per "
"crystal structure, depending on their acidic behavior, &etc; You can change "
"all that in the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko več pogledov na tabelo: klasični periodni sistem, kratek "
"periodni sistem, dolg periodni sistem &etc; Prav tako je mogoče spremeniti "
"shemo številčenja ali prikazati elemente po družinah, skupinah, kristalni "
"strukturi, glede na njihovo kislo obnašanje &etc; Vse to lahko spremenite v "
"meniju <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to know facts about a precise element, click on it in the table "
"and the information dialog will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvedeti dejstva o določenem elementu, kliknite nanj v preglednici "
"in prikazalo se bo pogovorno okno z informacijami."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Information dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno z informacijami</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Information dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno z informacijami</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can plot data using the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Plot Data...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. You choose "
"what you want to plot on the y-axis and a range of elements to plot that for "
"on the x-axis. The screenshot below shows the atomic mass of the elements 1 "
"to 10. Click the &nbsp;<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"swap-panels.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"<guibutton>Swap</guibutton> button between the axis panes to swap X and Y "
"axes."
msgstr ""
"Podatke lahko narišete z uporabo menijske postavke <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izriši podatke...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Izberete, kaj želite prikazati na osi y, in območje elementov, "
"za katere želite to prikazati na osi x. Spodnja slika prikazuje atomsko maso "
"elementov od 1 do 10. Kliknite &nbsp;<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"swap-panels.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>Zamenjaj osi X in Y</guibutton> gumb med "
"okenci osi za zamenjavo osi X in Y."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Plot Data dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno nariši podatke</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Plot Data dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno nariši podatke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Glossary (<menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Glossary..."
"</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>) explains the most important chemical words and "
"shows you pictures of the most common tools along with an explanation."
msgstr ""
"Besednjak (<menuchoice> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Besednjak...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>) pojasnjuje najpomembnejše kemijske besede in "
"prikazuje slike najpogostejših orodij skupaj z razlago."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Glossary</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Besednjak</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Glossary</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Besednjak</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kalzium;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kalzium;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview of &kalzium; usage"
msgstr "Pregled uporabe &kalzium;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; is very easy to use. It is specially designed for students of all "
"ages to use as a small and quick database."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; je zelo enostaven za uporabo. Namenjen je študentom vseh starosti "
"za uporabo kot majhna in hitra podatkovna zbirka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of &kalzium; in action:"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona, ki prikazuje &kalzium; v akciji:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; main screen, immediately after the first start"
msgstr "&kalzium; glavni zaslon, takoj po prvem zagonu"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; main screen"
msgstr "&kalzium; glavni zaslon"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "The information dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno z informacijami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The information dialog is accessed by clicking with the &LMB; on any "
"element. This is the place to get information about an element. With the "
"buttons at the bottom of the dialog you can change the element which is "
"displayed without closing the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Do pogovornega okna z informacijami dostopate tako, da kliknete z &LMB; na "
"kateri koli element. Na tem mestu lahko dobite informacije o elementu. Z "
"gumbi na dnu pogovornega okna lahko spremenite prikazani element, ne da bi "
"zaprli pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data Overview"
msgstr "Pregled podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Data Overview</guilabel> page tells you about different facts "
"related to the element."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Pregled podatkov</guilabel> so navedena različna "
"dejstva, povezana z elementom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the data available in &kalzium; you will see different radii of "
"the element. The covalent radius is the radius of a non charged atom of the "
"element in a molecule. The could for example be the O-H-distance in Water. "
"The atomic radius is the radius of an elemental atom, &eg; not bound to "
"anything. The van der Waals-radius is defined as the distance of two atoms "
"of the same sort in two equal molecules, for example two carbon-atoms in "
"propane. The last possible radius is the ionic radius including its charge."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od podatkov, ki so na voljo v &kalzium; boste videli različne radije "
"elementa. Kovalentni polmer je polmer nenabitega atoma elementa v molekuli. "
"Lahko je na primer razdalja O-H v vodi. Atomski polmer je polmer "
"elementarnega atoma, &eg; ni vezan na nič. Van der Waalsov radij je "
"opredeljen kot razdalja dveh atomov iste vrste v dveh enakih molekulah, na "
"primer dveh atomov ogljika v propanu. Zadnji možni polmer je ionski polmer "
"vključno z njegovim nabojem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mass of an element is the average mass of all isotopes in relation to "
"their percentage."
msgstr ""
"Masa elementa je povprečna masa vseh izotopov glede na njihov odstotek."

#. Tag: screeninfo
