msgstr "<phrase>&kalzium; pogovorno okno z informacijami</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bohr Orbitals"
msgstr "Bohrove orbitale"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Atom Model</guilabel> page displays the atomic shells. Every "
"orbit stands for a atomic shell and every yellow circle represents an "
"electron."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Modek atoma</guilabel> prikazuje atomske lupine. Vsaka "
"orbita predstavlja atomsko lupino in vsak rumen krogec predstavlja elektron."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Isotopes"
msgstr "Izotopi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Isotopes</guilabel> page presents information about the "
"isotopes of an element."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Izotopi</guilabel> predstavlja informacije o izotopih "
"elementa."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mass"
msgstr "Masa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "The mass of this isotope."
msgstr "Masa tega izotopa."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Neutrons"
msgstr "Nevtroni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of neutrons this isotope has."
msgstr "Število nevtronov, ki jih ima ta izotop."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Percentage"
msgstr "Delež"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The percentage of atoms occurring that are of this isotope type. Also called "
"abundance."
msgstr "Delež atomov te vrste izotopa. Imenuje se tudi obilje."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Half-life period"
msgstr "Razpolovni čas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only unstable isotopes have a half-life period. It is defined as the time in "
"which half the isotopes decay."
msgstr ""
"Samo nestabilni izotopi imajo razpolovni čas. Opredeljen je kot čas, v "
"katerem razpade polovica izotopov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Energy and Mode of Decay"
msgstr "Energija in način razpada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some isotopes are known to emit particle radiation under the process of "
"radioactive decay. Each decay transformation has a typical energy release, "
"which is listed along with the mode of decay."
msgstr ""
"Znano je, da nekateri izotopi oddajajo sevanje delcev v procesu "
"radioaktivnega razpada. Vsaka razpadna transformacija ima značilno "
"sproščanje energije, ki je navedena skupaj z načinom razpada."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spin and Parity"
msgstr "Spin in parnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "The spin of the nucleus and its parity."
msgstr "Spin jedra in njegova parnost."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Magnetic Moment"
msgstr "Magnetni moment"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The magnetic dipole moment of the nucleus. Measured in units of the nuclear "
"magneton."
msgstr "Magnetni dipolni moment jedra. Merjeno v enotah jedrskega magnetona."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Razno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Miscellaneous</guilabel> page tells you other information "
"about the current element, including when it was discovered and the origin "
"of the name."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Miscellaneous</guilabel> so na voljo druge informacije o "
"trenutnem elementu, vključno s tem, kdaj je bil odkrit, in izvorom imena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spectrum"
msgstr "Spekter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Spectrum</guilabel> page shows you elements spectrum. You can "
"choose the range of the wavelengths, units and type of the spectrum. The "
"intensity table can be seen at the right bottom part of the page."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Spekter</guilabel> je prikazan spekter elementov. "
"Izberete lahko območje valovnih dolžin, enote in vrsto spektra. preglednica "
"intenzivnosti je na voljo na desnem spodnjem delu strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extra Information"
msgstr "Dodatni podatki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Extra information</guilabel> page gives you the links to the "
"element pages on Wikipedia, <ulink url=\"https://education.jlab.org/"
"\">Jefferson Lab</ulink>, and <ulink url=\"https://www.webelements.com/"
"\">WebElements</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Dodatni podatki</guilabel> so na voljo povezave do "
"strani elementov v Wikipediji, <ulink url=\"https://education.jlab.org/"
"\">Jefferson Lab</ulink> in <ulink url=\"https://www.webelements.com/"
"\">WebElements</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:323 index.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tables"
msgstr "Periodni sistemi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The periodic table can be presented in various ways. You can switch the "
"table view from <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu or toolbar drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Periodni sistem lahko predstavimo na različne načine. Pogled tabele lahko "
"preklopite iz menija <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> ali spustnega seznama orodne "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Tables</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu can be used to change the "
"table shown:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednje možnosti v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Periodni sistemi</guisubmenu></menuchoice> lahko uporabite za "
"spremembo prikazane tabele:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Classic Periodic Table</term>"
msgstr "<term>Klasična periodna tabela</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Display</action> the classic periodic table with all elements."
msgstr "<action>Prikaži</action> klasični periodni sistem z vsemi elementi."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Short Periodic Table</term>"
msgstr "<term>Kratek periodni sistem</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340 index.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Display</action> a periodic table without transition elements."
msgstr "<action>Prikaži</action> periodni sistem brez prehodnih elementov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Long Periodic Table</term>"
msgstr "<term>Dolg periodni sistem</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348 index.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Display</action> a periodic table with inner transition elements (f-"
"elements) embedded."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaz</action> periodnega sistema z vgrajenimi notranjimi "
"prehodnimi elementi (f-elementi)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Transition Elements</term>"
msgstr "<term>Prehodni Elementi</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356 index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Display</action> a periodic table only with transition elements."
msgstr "<action>Prikaži</action> periodni sistem samo s prehodnimi elementi."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>DZ Periodic Table</term>"
msgstr "<term>Periodni sistem DZ</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This item represents the table the DZ <foreignphrase lang=\"de\">Deutscher "
"Zentralausschuss</foreignphrase> \"German Central Committee\" suggests."
msgstr ""
"Ta postavka predstavlja tabelo, ki jo predlaga DZ <foreignphrase lang=\"de"
"\">Deutscher Zentralausschuss</foreignphrase> \"Nemški centralni odbor\"."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Numeration"
msgstr "Številčenje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The numeration is the way of numbering the 18 groups of the periodic table. "
"You can change the numeration to <guilabel>IUPAC</guilabel>, <guilabel>old "
"IUPAC</guilabel> or <guilabel>CAS</guilabel>, or you can switch it off "
"entirely."
msgstr ""
"Številčenje je način oštevilčenja 18 skupin periodnega sistema. Številčenje "
"lahko spremenite v <guilabel>IUPAC</guilabel>, <guilabel>star IUPAC</"
"guilabel> ali <guilabel>CAS</guilabel>, lahko pa ga tudi popolnoma izklopite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Numeration</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu can be used to "
"change the numeration shown:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednje možnosti v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Številčenje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> lahko uporabite za "
"spremembo prikazanega številčenja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>No Numeration</guimenuitem>: if this option is active, no "
"period-numeration will be in effect."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Brz številčenja</guimenuitem>: če je ta možnost aktivna, ne bo "
"veljalo nobeno številčenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>IUPAC</guimenuitem> (default) is the <firstterm>International "
"Union of Pure and Applied Chemistry</firstterm>. This is an organization "
"which defines most of the standards for chemical concerns. The new IUPAC "
"system numbers each column with Arabic numbers from 1 (one) through 18 "
"(eighteen)."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>IUPAC</guimenuitem> (privzeto) je <firstterm>International "
"Union of Pure and Applied Chemistry</firstterm>. To je organizacija, ki "
"opredeljuje večino standardov za kemijske zadeve. Novi sistem IUPAC vsak "
"stolpec številči z arabskimi številkami od 1 (ena) do 18 (osemnajst)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>CAS</guimenuitem> is the <firstterm>Chemical Abstracts Service</"
"firstterm>. In the CAS system the letters A and B were designated to main "
"group elements (A) and transition elements (B). Though the <acronym>IUPAC</"
"acronym> numeration is the official, the <acronym>CAS</acronym> numeration "
"is what is still used in classrooms and laboratories."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>CAS</guimenuitem> je <firstterm>Chemical Abstracts Service</"
"firstterm>. V sistemu CAS sta bili črki A in B označeni za elemente glavne "
"skupine (A) in prehodne elemente (B). Čeprav je uradno številčenje "
"<acronym>IUPAC</acronym>, se v učilnicah in laboratorijih še vedno uporablja "
"številčenje <acronym>CAS</acronym>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Old IUPAC</guimenuitem> system labeled columns with Roman "
"numerals followed by either the letter <quote>A</quote> or <quote>B</quote>. "
"Columns were numbered such that columns one through seven were numbered "
"<quote>IA</quote> through <quote>VIIA</quote>, columns 8 through 10 were "
"labeled <quote>VIIIA</quote>, columns 11 through 17 were numbered <quote>IB</"
"quote> through <quote>VIIB</quote> and column 18 was numbered <quote>VIII</"
"quote>. Because of the confusion the old IUPAC and the CAS system created, "
"the IUPAC adopted their new system."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Stari IUPAC</guimenuitem> je označeval stolpce z rimskimi "
"številkami, ki jim je sledila črka <quote>A</quote> ali <quote>B</quote>. "
"Stolpci so bili oštevilčeni tako, da so bili stolpci od prvega do sedmega "
"oštevilčeni od <quote>IA</quote> do <quote>VIIA</quote>, stolpci od 8 do 10 "
"so bili označeni z <quote>VIIIA</quote>, stolpci od 11 do 17 so bili "
"oštevilčeni od <quote>IB</quote> do <quote>VIIB</quote>, stolpec 18 pa je "
"bil oštevilčen z <quote>VIII</quote>. Zaradi zmede, ki sta jo povzročala "
"stari sistem IUPAC in sistem CAS, je IUPAC sprejel svoj novi sistem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color schemes"
msgstr "Barvne sheme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; can show you which elements are where with regard to their "
"Periodic <quote>block</quote> and <quote>group</quote>, their behavior with "
"acid and which state of matter (&ie; solid/liquid/vapor) they are in at a "
"given temperature."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; vam lahko pokaže, kateri elementi so kje glede na njihov periodni "
"<quote>blok</quote> in <quote>skupino</quote>, njihovo obnašanje s kislino "
"in v katerem stanju snovi (&ie; trdno/tekoče/parno) so pri določeni "
"temperaturi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Color schemes can be changed in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Scheme</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu, toolbar drop-down list, "
"or <link linkend=\"view_tab\">View</link> tab of the Sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Barvne sheme lahko spremenite v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Shema</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, spustnem seznamu orodne "
"vrstice ali <link linkend=\"view_tab\">Pogled</link> zavihka stranske "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Monochrome</guimenuitem>: all the elements have the same color. "
"You can change the default color by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kalzium;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> and "
"going to the <guilabel>Schemes</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Enobarvno</guimenuitem>: vsi elementi imajo enako barvo. "
"Privzeto barvo lahko spremenite tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguracija "
"&kalzium;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in odprete stran <guilabel>Sheme</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Blocks</guimenuitem>: displays a color for each block."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Bloki</guimenuitem>: prikaže barvo za vsak blok."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Iconic</guimenuitem>: displays icons for each element."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Ikone</guimenuitem>: prikaže ikone za vsak element."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Family</guimenuitem>: represents each of the nine families with "
"a color."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Družina</guimenuitem>: predstavlja vsako od devetih družin z "
"barvo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Groups</guimenuitem>: displays a color for each group. A group "
"is a vertical column in the periodic table of the elements. There are 18 "
"groups in the standard periodic table. Elements in a group have similar "
"configurations of their valence shell electrons, which gives them similar "
"properties."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Skupine</guimenuitem>: prikaže barvo za vsako skupino. Skupina "
"je navpični stolpec v periodnem sistemu elementov. V standardnem periodnem "
"sistemu je 18 skupin. Elementi v skupini imajo podobne konfiguracije "
"elektronov v valenčni lupini, kar jim daje podobne lastnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Colors</guimenuitem>: Nice colors without meaning. (From the "
"<ulink url=\"https://openbabel.org/wiki/Main_Page\">Open Babel</ulink> "
"project)."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Barve</guimenuitem>: Lepe barve brez pomena. (Iz projekta "
"<ulink url=\"https://openbabel.org/wiki/Main_Page\">Open Babel</ulink>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Gradients</title>"
msgstr "<title>Prelivi</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The gradient views displays the elements according to a property you can "
"select below and with a gradient colored scheme. The elements for which the "
"data is not available are displayed in gray."
msgstr ""
"Prelivni pogledi prikažejo elemente glede na lastnost, ki jo lahko izberete "
"spodaj, in z gradientno barvno shemo. Elementi, za katere podatki niso na "
"voljo, so prikazani v sivi barvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gradients can be changed in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Gradients</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu, toolbar drop-down "
"list, or <link linkend=\"view_tab\">View</link> tab of the Sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Prelive lahko spremenite v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prelivi</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, spustnem seznamu orodne "
"vrstice ali <link linkend=\"view_tab\">Pogled</link> zavihka stranske "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Gradient for Covalent Radius</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Preliv za kovalentni polmer</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Gradient for Covalent Radius</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Preliv za kovalentni polmer</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Implemented are the following gradients (some listed items are clickable):"
msgstr ""
"Izvedeni so naslednji gradienti (nekatere naštete elemente je mogoče "
"klikniti):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>None</guimenuitem>: do not use gradients."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Brez</guimenuitem>: ne uporabi prelivov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/State_of_matter"
"\"><guimenuitem>State of matter</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/State_of_matter"
"\"><guimenuitem>Agregatno stanje</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Covalent_Radius"
"\"><guimenuitem>Covalent Radius</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Covalent_Radius"
"\"><guimenuitem>Kovalentni polmer</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Van_der_Waals_radius"
"\"><guimenuitem>Van der Waals</guimenuitem></ulink>: gradient by van der "
"Waals radius."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Van_der_Waals_radius"
"\"><guimenuitem>Van der Waals</guimenuitem></ulink>: preliv glede na Van der "
"Waals polmer."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atomic_Mass\"><guimenuitem>Atomic "
"Mass</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atomic_Mass"
"\"><guimenuitem>Atomska masa</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boiling_Point"
"\"><guimenuitem>Boiling Point</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boiling_Point"
"\"><guimenuitem>Vrelišče</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melting_Point"
"\"><guimenuitem>Melting Point</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melting_Point"
"\"><guimenuitem>Tališče</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electronegativity"
