"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ionization_energy"
"\"><guimenuitem>First Ionization</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ionization_energy"
"\"><guimenuitem>Prva ionizacija</guimenuitem></ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "Orodja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "Molecular Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik molekul"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Molecular Editor allows you to view and edit molecules using <ulink url="
"\"https://avogadro.cc\">Avogadro 2</ulink> libraries."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik molekul omogoča pregledovanje in urejanje molekul z uporabo "
"knjižnic <ulink url=\"https://avogadro.cc\">Avogadro 2</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the control panel on the left, you can change the view parameters, "
"edit molecule, or measure molecules. There are three tabs on this panel: "
"<guilabel>Display</guilabel>, <guilabel>Edit</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Measure</guilabel>. At the top of the window, there is a control "
"to select the viewer <guilabel>Style:</guilabel> (can be <guimenuitem>Ball "
"and Stick</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Licorice</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Van der Waals</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Van der Waals (AO)</"
"guimenuitem> (<abbrev>AO</abbrev> means <quote>Ambient Occlusion</quote>), "
"or <guimenuitem>Wireframe</guimenuitem>). The buttons along the bottom of "
"the window can be used to <guibutton>Load Molecule</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>Download New Molecules</guibutton>, <guibutton>Save Molecule</"
"guibutton>, and <guibutton>Close</guibutton> the window. The downloaded "
"files will be saved in your <filename class=\"directory\">Documents</"
"filename> folder from where you can load them into the editor."
msgstr ""
"Na nadzorni plošči na levi strani lahko spreminjate parametre pogleda, "
"urejate molekule ali merite molekule. Na tej plošči so trije zavihki: "
"<guilabel>Prikaz</guilabel>, <guilabel>Uredi</guilabel> in <guilabel>Izmeri</"
"guilabel>. Na vrhu okna je kontrolnik za izbiro pregledovalnika "
"<guilabel>Slog:</guilabel> (lahko je <guimenuitem>Ball and Stick</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Licorice</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Van der "
"Waals</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Van der Waals (AO)</guimenuitem> "
"(<abbrev>AO</abbrev> pomeni <quote>Ambient Occlusion</quote>) ali "
"<guimenuitem>Wireframe</guimenuitem>). Z gumbi na dnu okna lahko "
"<guibutton>Naloži molekulo</guibutton>, <guibutton>Prejmi nove molekule</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>Shrani molekulo</guibutton> in <guibutton>Zapri</"
"guibutton> okno. Prenesene datoteke bodo shranjene v mapo <filename class="
"\"directory\">Documents</filename>, od koder jih lahko naložite v "
"urejevalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Statistics</guilabel> pane shows name (if available), formula, and "
"weight of the molecule."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Podokno Statistika</guilabel> prikazuje ime (če je na voljo), "
"formulo in maso molekul."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Display</guilabel> tab can be used to view a loaded molecule. "
"By pressing the mouse pointer in the view, you can change the view point. "
"Use &LMB; to rotate molecule, &RMB; to move it, and &MMB; to zoom."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Prikaz</guilabel> lahko uporabite za ogled naložene "
"molekule. S pritiskom na kazalec miške v pogledu lahko spremenite točko "
"pogleda. Za vrtenje molekule uporabite &LMB;, za premikanje &RMB; in za "
"povečavo &MMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Edit</guilabel> tab allows you to edit the molecule. You can "
"add elements by choosing them in the <guilabel>Element</guilabel> drop-down "
"list then clicking with the &LMB; on the view panel on the right."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Uredi</guilabel> omogoča urejanje molekule. Elemente lahko "
"dodate tako, da jih izberete na spustnem seznamu <guilabel>Element</"
"guilabel>, nato pa kliknete z &LMB; na plošči za prikaz na desni strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Measure</guilabel> tab can be used to measure distances and "
"angles in the molecule. To make the measurement use the instructions shown "
"on the tab."
msgstr ""
"Z zavihkom <guilabel>Izmeri</guilabel> lahko merite razdalje in kote v "
"molekuli. Za merjenje uporabite navodila, ki so prikazana na zavihku."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Molecular Editor</quote>"
msgstr "<quote>Urejevalnik molekul</quote>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Isotope Table"
msgstr "preglednica izotopov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Isotope Table</guilabel> shows you the isotopes of the "
"elements."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Preglednica izotopov</guilabel> vam prikaže izotope elementov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are different kinds of isotopes, some are stable, some are not. The "
"unstable isotopes can decay as alpha-rays are two different beta-rays. These "
"differences are encoded by using different colors."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo različne vrste izotopov, nekateri so stabilni, drugi ne. "
"Nestabilni izotopi lahko razpadejo kot žarki alfa in dva različna žarka "
"beta. Te razlike so zakodirane z uporabo različnih barv."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Isotope Table</quote> window"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Preglednica izotopov</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; can display the isotopes of a range of elements"
msgstr "&kalzium; lahko prikaže izotope številnih elementov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plot Data"
msgstr "Izriši podatke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Plot Data</guilabel> dialog allows you to plot some "
"information about elements. The X-axis represents a range of elements (from "
"one number to a higher number). You set this range using the <guilabel>First "
"element:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Last element:</guilabel> fields on the "
"dialog. Click the &nbsp;<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"swap-panels.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"<guibutton>Swap</guibutton> button between the axis panes to swap X and Y "
"axes."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Izriši podatke</guilabel> lahko narišete "
"nekatere podatke o elementih. Os X predstavlja razpon elementov (od enega do "
"večjega števila). Ta razpon določite z uporabo polj <guilabel>Prvi element:</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Zadnji element:</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu. "
"Kliknite &nbsp;<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"swap-"
"panels.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"<guibutton>Zamenjaj osi X in Y</guibutton> gumb med okenci osi za zamenjavo "
"osi X in Y."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Plot Data</quote> Dialog"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Izriši podatke</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; can plot some data about a range of elements."
msgstr "&kalzium; lahko izriše nekaj podatkov o vrsti elementov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid "Perform Calculation"
msgstr "Izvedi izračune"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Perform Calculation...</guimenuitem> is the &kalzium; "
"calculator. This calculator contains a variety of calculators for different "
"tasks performing different calculations."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Izvedi izračun...</guimenuitem> je &kalzium; kalkulator. Ta "
"kalkulator vsebuje različne kalkulatorje za različna opravila, ki opravljajo "
"različne izračune."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can find the following calculators in &kalzium;:"
msgstr "Naslednje kalkulatorje najdete v razdelku &kalzium;:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Molecular mass calculator"
msgstr "Računalo molekulske mase"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This calculator helps you calculate the molecular masses of different "
"molecules."
msgstr "Ta kalkulator vam pomaga izračunati molekulske mase različnih molekul."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can specify short form of the molecule names add more such aliases."
msgstr ""
"Navedete lahko kratke oblike imen molekul in dodate več takšnih vzdevkov."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Molecular mass calculator</quote> dialog"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Računala molekulske mase</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; calculates molecular mass of phenol."
msgstr "&kalzium; izračuna molekulsko maso fenola."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Concentrations calculator"
msgstr "Računalo koncentracij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can calculate quantities which include:"
msgstr "Izračunate lahko količine, ki vključujejo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amount of solute"
msgstr "Količina topljenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Density of solvent"
msgstr "Gostota topljenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Density of solute"
msgstr "Gostota topila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a wide range of units to choose from and different methods to "
"specify quantities."
msgstr ""
"Izbirate lahko med številnimi enotami in različnimi metodami za določanje "
"količin."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Concentrations calculator</quote> dialog"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Računalo koncentracij</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; calculates solution parameters."
msgstr "&kalzium; izračuna parametre topila."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid "Nuclear calculator"
msgstr "Jedrsko računalo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This calculator makes use of the nuclear data available in &kalzium; to "
"predict the expected masses of a material after time."
msgstr ""
"Ta kalkulator uporablja jedrske podatke, ki so na voljo v programu &kalzium; "
"za napovedovanje pričakovanih mas snovi po določenem času."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Nuclear calculator</quote> dialog"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Jedrsko računalo</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; calculates parameters of uranium decay."
msgstr "&kalzium; izračuna parametre razpada urana."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gas calculator"
msgstr "Računalo plinov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This calculator can calculate the values of Temperature, pressure, volume, "
"amount of gas &etc; for various ideal as well as non-ideal gases."
msgstr ""
"Ta kalkulator lahko izračuna vrednosti temperature, tlaka, prostornine, "
"količine plina &etc; za različne idealne in neidealne pline."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Gas calculator</quote> dialog"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Računalo plinov</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; calculates gas parameters."
msgstr "&kalzium; izračuna parametre plinov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid "Titration calculator"
msgstr "Računalo titracije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This calculator tries to find out the equivalence point of a pH-meter "
"followed titration best fitting it with an hyperbolic tangent. You can also "
"let it solve an equilibrium system of equations and see how the "
"concentration of a species changes in function of another one."
msgstr ""
"To računalo poskuša najti ekvivalenčno točko meritve s pH metrom tako, da "
"podatkom prilega hiperbolično tangento. Pustite mu lahko tudi, da reši "
"ravnotežni sistem enačb in vidite kako se koncentracija zvrsti spremeni kot "
"funkcija druge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two tabs on the calculator page, namely:"
msgstr "Na strani računala sta dva zavihka, in sicer:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Experimental values"
msgstr "Eksperimentalne vrednosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use this calculator to draw the plot of your experimental data "
"obtained during a titration and find out the volume of equivalence. It's "
"strongly recommended to insert a even number of points, because of the best "
"fit algorithm, sorted by volume (the <guilabel>X axis:</guilabel> value)."
msgstr ""
"S tem računalom lahko narišete graf eksperimentalnih podatkov, pridobljenih "
"med titracijo, in ugotovite prostornino ekvivalence. Zaradi algoritma za "
"najboljše prileganje je zelo priporočljivo vstaviti sodo število točk, "
"razvrščenih po prostornini (vrednost na osi <guilabel>X:</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid "Theoretical Equations"
msgstr "Teoretične enačbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can fill the table with the equations you have previously obtained "
"for the chemical equilibrium."
msgstr ""
"V tabelo lahko vnesete enačbe, ki ste jih prej dobili za kemijsko ravnovesje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, if you have this reaction <emphasis>A + B -> C + D</emphasis> "
"then you will have the equation <emphasis>K=(C*D)/(A*B)</emphasis> so you "
"must write <userinput>K</userinput> in the <guilabel>Parameter</guilabel> "
"column and <userinput>(C*D)/(A*B)</userinput> in the <guilabel>Value</"
"guilabel> column. If you want to assign a known value to a parameter you can "
"simply write the numeric value in the <guilabel>Value</guilabel> field."
msgstr ""
"Če imate na primer to reakcijo <emphasis>A + B -> C + D</emphasis>, potem "
"boste imeli enačbo <emphasis>K=(C*D)/(A*B)</emphasis>, zato morate v stolpec "
"<guilabel>Parameter</guilabel> zapisati <userinput>K</userinput> in v "
"stolpec <guilabel>Vrednost</guilabel> <userinput>(C*D)/(A*B)</userinput>. Če "
"želite parametru pripisati znano vrednost, lahko preprosto zapišete "
"številčno vrednost v polje <guilabel>Vrednost</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid "For example, you can use the system"
msgstr "Uporabite lahko na primer sistem"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "A=(C*D)/(B*K)"
msgstr "A=(C*D)/(B*K)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid "K=10^-3"
msgstr "K=10^-3"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "C=OH"
msgstr "C=OH"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "OH=(10^-14)/H"
msgstr "OH=(10^-14)/H"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid "H=10^-4"
msgstr "H=10^-4"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid "B=6*(10^-2)"
msgstr "B=6*(10^-2)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then you have to write <userinput>D</userinput> as <guilabel>X axis:</"
"guilabel> and <userinput>A</userinput> as <guilabel>Y axis:</guilabel>: so "
"you will find out how the concentration of A changes as a function of D "
"concentration."
msgstr ""
"Potem morate <userinput>D</userinput> zapisati kot <guilabel>os X:</"
"guilabel> in <userinput>A</userinput> kot <guilabel>os Y:</guilabel>: tako "
"boste ugotovili, kako se koncentracija A spreminja kot funkcija "
"koncentracije D."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please don't use parenthesis for exponents: <userinput>10^-3</userinput> is "
"correct, while <userinput>10^(-3)</userinput> is wrong."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo, ne uporabljajte oklepajev za eksponente: <userinput>10^-3</"
"userinput> je pravilno, <userinput>10^(-3)</userinput> pa napačno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results can be visualized by pressing <guibutton>Draw Plot</guibutton> "
"button. The plot shows in red the curve that comes from theoretical "
"equations, in blue the experimental points, and in green the approximated "
"curve for experimental points. You can save the plot as &SVG; image."
msgstr ""
"Rezultate lahko prikažete s pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Izriši polje</"
"guibutton>. Na grafu je z rdečo barvo prikazana krivulja iz teoretičnih "
"enačb, z modro so prikazane eksperimentalne točke, z zeleno pa približana "
"krivulja za eksperimentalne točke. Sliko lahko shranite kot &SVG; sliko."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Titration calculator</quote> dialog"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Računalo titracije</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid "Predefined example of titration results."
msgstr "Vnaprej določen primer rezultatov titracije."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Equation Balancer"
msgstr "Urejevalnik enačb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Equation Balancer</guilabel> enables the user to solve "
"chemical equations. This is an example:"
msgstr ""
"S programom <guilabel>urejevalnik enačb</guilabel> lahko uporabnik urejuje "
"kemijske enačbe. To je primer:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid "aH2O + bCO2 -> cH2CO3"
msgstr "aH2O + bCO2 -> cH2CO3"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The computed equation will be displayed on the top of the window. As you can "
"see in the first example you can also define the value of one or more "
"coefficients. The other coefficients will be adjusted. Furthermore, it is "
"possible to use brackets around elements or electronic charges as shown in "
"the last two examples."
msgstr ""
"Izračunana enačba se prikaže na vrhu okna. Kot lahko vidite v prvem primeru, "
"lahko določite tudi vrednost enega ali več koeficientov. Drugi koeficienti "
"bodo prilagojeni. Poleg tega je mogoče okoli elementov ali elektronskih "
"nabojev uporabiti oklepaje, kot je prikazano v zadnjih dveh primerih."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:751
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Equation Balancer</quote> dialog"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Urejevalnik enačb</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; calculates equation balance."
msgstr "&kalzium; izračuna ravnotežje enačbe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Risk/Security Phrases"
msgstr "Stavki R/S"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>R/S Phrases</guilabel>, also known as Risk and Safety "
"Statements, R/S statements, R/S numbers, and R/S sentences, is a system of "
"hazard codes and phrases for labeling dangerous chemicals and compounds. The "
"R/S phrase of a compound consists of a risk part (R) and a safety part (S), "
"each followed by a combination of numbers. Each number corresponds to a "
"phrase. The phrase corresponding to the letter/number combination has the "
"same meaning in different languages."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Stavki R/S</guilabel>, znani tudi kot izjave o tveganju in "
"varnosti, izjave R/S, številke R/S in vrstice R/S, so sistem kod nevarnosti "
"in stavkov za označevanje nevarnih kemikalij in spojin. Besedna zveza R/S je "
"sestavljena iz dela o tveganju (R - risk) in dela o varnosti (S - safety), "
"ki jima sledi kombinacija številk. Vsaka številka ustreza stavku. Besedna "
"zveza, ki ustreza kombinaciji črka/številka, ima v različnih jezikih enak "
"pomen."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>R/S Phrases</quote> window"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Stavki R/S</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalzium; can display Risk/Security Phrases"
msgstr "&kalzium; lahko prikaže stavke o tveganju/varnosti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:782
#, no-c-format
msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "Besednjak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Glossary</guilabel> gives you definitions of the most used "
"tools in chemistry as well as some knowledge data. On the left side of the "
"windows you can see the tree of items. On top, there are chemical terms, "
"below that there is a second tree of laboratory-tools."
msgstr ""
"V <guilabel>Besednjaku</guilabel> so na voljo opredelitve najpogosteje "
"uporabljenih orodij v kemiji in nekateri podatki o znanju. Na levi strani "
"oken je prikazano drevo elementov. Na vrhu so kemijski izrazi, pod njimi pa "
"je drugo drevo laboratorijskih orodij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the top of the widget you can see a searchbar. If you type in the bar the "
"trees will be adjusted immediately. The small button in the right end of the "
"searchbar will clear it."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu gradnika je prikazana iskalna vrstica. Če vnesete vrstico, se "
"drevesa takoj prilagodijo. Z majhnim gumbom na desnem koncu iskalne vrstice "
"jo lahko izbrišete."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Glossary</quote>"
msgstr "<quote>Besednjak</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Tables</guilabel> shows you the tables for Greek alphabet "
"which is used to denote some chemical and physical entities, and for Latin "
"prefixes and Roman numbers which correspond to common Arabic numbers."
msgstr ""
"V <guilabel>Preglednice</guilabel> so prikazane tabele za grško abecedo, ki "
"se uporablja za označevanje nekaterih kemijskih in fizikalnih entitet, ter "
"za latinske predpone in rimske številke, ki ustrezajo običajnim arabskim "
"številkam."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Tables</quote> window"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Preglednice</quote>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sidebar"
msgstr "Stranska vrstica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Overview</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pregled</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Overview</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pregled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:825
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Overview</guilabel> tab is the first one and it shows you an "
"overview of the element the mouse is over."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Pregled</guilabel> je prvi zavihek in prikazuje pregled "
"elementa, nad katerim je miška."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr "Pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:831
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>View</guilabel> tab is the second in the navigation panel."
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel> je drugi na navigacijski plošči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid "You are first presented with the following icons and text:"
msgstr "Najprej se prikažejo naslednje ikone in besedilo:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>State of Matter</quote> Dialog"
msgstr "pogovorno okno <quote>Agregatno stanje</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; can show you which elements are solid/liquid/vaporous at a given "
"temperature."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; vam lahko pokaže, kateri elementi so pri določeni temperaturi "
"trdni/tekoči/parni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>View</guilabel> tab can be used to filter PSE. For example, "
"this feature allows you to explore the elements of the set time period. This "
"is great for getting a feel for how the PSE evolved over time, as more and "
"more elements were discovered. Choose <guimenuitem>Discovery date</"
"guimenuitem> from <guilabel>Gradient:</guilabel> list. If you move the "
"slider you will notice that color of some elements disappear if you move it "
"to the left and reappear if you move it to the right. Furthermore the number "
"will change constantly."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel> lahko uporabite za filtriranje sistema "
"PSE. Ta funkcija vam na primer omogoča raziskovanje elementov v določenem "
"časovnem obdobju. To je odličen pripomoček za spoznavanje razvoja sistema "
"PSE skozi čas, ko je bilo odkritih vedno več elementov. Izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Datum odkritja</guimenuitem> s seznama <guilabel>Preliv:</"
"guilabel>. Če premikate drsnik, boste opazili, da barva nekaterih elementov "
"izgine, če ga premaknete v levo, in se ponovno pojavi, če ga premaknete v "
"desno. Poleg tega se število stalno spreminja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number represents the date you are looking at. If you move the slider to "
"&eg; 1856 you will only see the elements which where known in the year 1856."
msgstr ""
"Številka predstavlja datum, ki ga gledate. Če premaknete drsnik na &eg;. "
"1856 boste videli le elemente, ki so bili znani v letu 1856."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:861
#, no-c-format
msgid "the <quote>Discovery date</quote> gradient"
msgstr "preliv <quote>Datum odkritja</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid "The PSE back in time (elements known in 1856)"
msgstr "PSE v preteklosti (elementi, znani leta 1856)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:874
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kalzium;"
msgstr "Konfiguracija &kalzium;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; has many configuration options, which you can access by opening "
"the configuration dialog by selecting <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kalzium;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"from the menu."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; ima številne možnosti konfiguracije, do katerih lahko dostopate "
"tako, da odprete pogovorno okno konfiguracije z izbiro <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguracija &kalzium;...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> v meniju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:882 index.docbook:896 index.docbook:910 index.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &kalzium; Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno &kalzium; Konfiguriraj"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid "Schemes"
msgstr "Sheme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:892
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Schemes</guilabel> tab, you can change the different colors "
"for each scheme."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Sheme</guilabel> lahko spremenite različne barve za "
"vsako shemo."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Gradients</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prelivi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instead of using a linear gradient to display the given property of an "
"element in the periodic table, &kalzium; can also use a logarithmic gradient."
msgstr ""
"Namesto uporabe linearnega gradienta za prikaz dane lastnosti elementa v "
"periodnem sistemu, lahko &kalzium; uporablja tudi logaritemski gradient."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Gradients</guilabel> tab, you can check the properties you "
"want to have displayed with a logarithmic gradient."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Prelivi</guilabel> lahko preverite lastnosti, ki jih "
"želite prikazati z logaritemskim prelivom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also choose <guilabel>Maximal Value Color:</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Minimal Value Color:</guilabel> for the gradient."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi <guilabel>Barva največje vrednosti:</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Barva najmanjše vrednosti:</guilabel> za preliv."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid "Units"
msgstr "Enote"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Units</guilabel> tab, you can choose the units for energy, "
"length and temperature. You can select if you prefer electronvolts (eV), "
"kilojoule per mole (kJ/mol), joule per mole (J/mol) or joules (J) by "
"default. For length set picometers (pm), nanometers (nm) or &Aring;"
"ngstr&ouml;m (&Aring;) as default. The temperature is in kelvin by default "
"but you can change to Celsius (°C), Fahrenheit (°F) and Réaumur (°Ré)."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Enote</guilabel> lahko izberete enote za energijo, "
"dolžino in temperaturo. Privzeto lahko izberete, ali želite elektronvolte "
"(eV), kilodžule na mol (kJ/mol), džul na mol (J/mol) ali džule (J). Za "
"dolžino privzeto nastavite pikometre (pm), nanometre (nm) ali &Aring;"
"ngstr&ouml;m (&Aring;). Temperatura je privzeto v kelvinih, vendar jo lahko "
"spremenite v Celzija (°C), Fahrenheita (°F) in Réaumurja (°Ré)."

