#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the world of science, the progress is quite fast. If you ever find an "
"incorrect or missing value, please drop me an email."
msgstr ""
"V svetu znanosti je napredek precej hiter. Če najdete napačno ali manjkajočo "
"vrednost, mi pišite po e-pošti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find some bugs or give some suggestions."
msgstr "Poiščite nekaj napak ali podajte nekaj predlogov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you find any bugs in the program, or have a few suggestions for "
"improvements, please let me know at &Carsten.Niehaus.mail;."
msgstr ""
"Če v programu odkrijete napake ali imate nekaj predlogov za izboljšave, mi "
"to sporočite na &Carsten.Niehaus.mail;."

